---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Documentation - DEML Platform">
  <div class="dashboard-page-container">
    <div class="dashboard-content-area">
      <div class="page-inner-wrapper">
        <header class="docs-hero">
          <div  class="u-style-58adc5">
            <span class="badge-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span  class="u-style-486a44">Developer Portal</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="docs-title">API Gateway & Integrations</h1>
          <p class="docs-subtitle">
            The central nervous system for your MLOps workflows. Seamlessly connect your
            infrastructure, stream telemetry, and interface with powerful models through our secure
            endpoints.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="docs-bento-grid page-inner-wrapper">
          <div class="docs-bento-card docs-bento-full">
            <div class="bento-header">
              <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">vpn_key</span>
              <h2>Authentication & Access</h2>
            </div>
            <p  class="u-style-7f7d6d">
              Secure access to our high-throughput pipelines requires an API key. Register an account,
              generate a secure token in your user profile, and pass it in the Authorization header.
            </p>
            <div class="code-block-premium">
              <div class="code-header">HTTP Header</div>
              <pre><code>Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-bento-card">
            <div class="bento-header">
              <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">input</span>
              <h2>Data Ingestion</h2>
            </div>
            <p  class="u-style-efd290">
              High-throughput endpoint optimized for receiving batched or streaming data from
              distributed pipelines like Apache Spark or Databricks.
            </p>
            <div class="endpoint-badge">
              <span class="method">POST</span>
              <span class="path">/api/v1/ingest</span>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block-premium u-style-5ab468" >
              <div class="code-header">cURL Request</div>
              <pre><code>curl -X POST https://backend.deml.app/api/v1/ingest \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123; "batch_id": "123", "records": [&#123;"feature1": 1.0&#125;] &#125;'</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-bento-card">
            <div class="bento-header">
              <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">model_training</span>
              <h2>Real-time Inference</h2>
            </div>
            <p  class="u-style-efd290">
              Low-latency endpoint for model inference, ideal for Kubernetes sidecars or deep learning
              services calling models directly.
            </p>
            <div class="endpoint-badge">
              <span class="method">POST</span>
              <span class="path">/api/v1/predict</span>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block-premium u-style-5ab468" >
              <div class="code-header">cURL Request</div>
              <pre><code>curl -X POST https://backend.deml.app/api/v1/predict \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123; "model_version": "v2", "inputs": [0.5, 0.2] &#125;'</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-bento-card">
            <div class="bento-header">
              <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">terminal</span>
              <h2>Native Integrations</h2>
            </div>
            <p  class="u-style-efd290">
              We provide native support and documentation for integrating with the industry's leading
              tools, including:
            </p>
            <ul  class="u-style-358aff">
              <li><strong>Kubernetes:</strong> Connect via CRDs or sidecar proxies.</li>
              <li><strong>TensorFlow:</strong> Stream using <code>tf.data.Dataset</code>.</li>
              <li><strong>Apache Spark:</strong> Write DataFrames directly.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-bento-card">
            <div class="bento-header">
              <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">security</span>
              <h2>Enterprise Security</h2>
            </div>
            <p  class="u-style-efd290">
              All tenant data is cryptographically isolated using strict multi-tenancy rules and
              enforced via our strict 30-day data retention policy.
              <strong>API Keys</strong> can only be managed exclusively through the user interface
              under your Settings panel. For ultimate security, keys are displayed only once upon
              creation and are immediately hashed in the database using SHA-256. <br /><br />
              Our infrastructure leverages strict Google Distroless-like multi-stage deployments
              (e.g., chainguard nginx) to eliminate shell-based attack surfaces. Data sent to our
              ingestion endpoints feeds directly into Redpanda message brokers, ensuring your
              analytics dashboard displays a fully unified, multi-tenant view of your infrastructure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
.dashboard-page-container {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
  background-color: var(--bg-color);
  color: var(--text-color);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.docs-hero {
  position: relative;
  margin: 0 auto 56px auto;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 32px 0;

  .docs-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--hero-title-color, var(--text-color));
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 704px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
}

.docs-bento-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  max-width: var(--container-max-width, 1152px);
  margin: 0 auto 56px auto;

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

.docs-bento-card {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 32px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;

  &:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: var(--crayola-blue);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .bento-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;

    .material-icons {
      font-size: 32px;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      color: var(--crayola-blue);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-color);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
  }
}

.docs-bento-full {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
}

.code-block-premium {
  background: var(--jet-black, #121212);
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  overflow: hidden;

  .code-header {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--carrot-orange, #ff9100);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;

    &::before {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--carrot-orange, #ff9100);
      box-shadow: 0 0 9px var(--carrot-orange, #ff9100);
    }
  }

  pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    overflow-x: auto;

    code {
      color: #e0e0e0;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      white-space: pre-wrap !important;
      word-wrap: break-word !important;
    }
  }
}

.endpoint-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: 8px 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  width: fit-content;

  .method {
    color: var(--success-color, #4caf50);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .path {
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
